      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "许褚"
      ],
      "text": "丞相发笑为哪般？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00025",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "曹操"
      ],
      "text": "笑只笑周郎见识浅，孔明袖内少机关。此处若有人和马，只恐性命难保全。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00026",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖内喊声〗。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00027",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "曹操"
      ],
      "text": "一言未尽人呐喊，旌旗招展心胆寒！",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00028",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹操"
      ],
      "text": "许褚，看看是什么人的旗号？",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00029",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "许褚"
      ],
      "text": "遵命！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00030",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "许褚看。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00031",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "许褚"
      ],
      "text": "乃是“关”字旗号。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00032",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹操"
      ],
      "text": "待我谢天谢地。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00033",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "许褚"
      ],
      "text": "事到如今，还谢的什么天地？",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00034",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹操"
      ],
      "text": "那关云长曾许我三不死，难道今日一死也不饶么？",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00035",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "许褚"
      ],
      "text": "我等杀不得了。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00036",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹操"
      ],
      "text": "不用你们杀了。就在此地歇息歇息。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00037",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "许褚"
      ],
      "text": "遵命。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00038",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四龙套、张辽、许褚、曹洪同席地坐。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00039",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮流水板",
      "speakers": [
        "曹操"
      ],
      "text": "听说来了关美髯，不由孟德喜心间。走上前来把礼见，问声君侯驾可安？",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00040",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "曹操打躬。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00041",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "关平",
        "周仓"
      ],
      "text": "曹操到！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00042",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "内西皮导板",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "耳旁厢又听得人嘶马闹，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00043",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "关羽上。关平、周仓、关羽同上高台，同亮相。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00044",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "展蚕眉睁凤眼仔细观瞧。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00045",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹操"
      ],
      "text": "君侯，别来无恙啊？哈哈哈……",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00046",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "狭路上莫不是冤家来到，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00047",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹操"
      ],
      "text": "故友相逢，怎说冤家二字？言重了哇！哈哈哈……",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00048",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "奉军令谁认你旧日故交！",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00049",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹操"
      ],
      "text": "君侯哇！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00050",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "曹操"
      ],
      "text": "曹孟德在马上满脸赔笑，尊一声二君侯细听根苗：在赤壁中火攻败兵来到，望君侯开大恩放我回朝。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00051",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "三国中论奸雄算你曹操，一派的假殷勤袖内藏刀。俺今日用兵时何必发笑？奉军令捉拿你怎肯相饶！",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00052",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "曹操"
      ],
      "text": "我中了小周郎苦肉计巧，https://scripts.xikao.com/play/030960032022-10-07只烧得众兵丁皮开肉焦。只剩下十八骑败兵来到，二君侯若不信仔细观瞧。",
      "text_length": 93
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00053",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "周将！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00054",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "周仓"
      ],
      "text": "在！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00055",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "查看曹操还有多少人马？",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00056",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "周仓"
      ],
      "text": "啊！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00057",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "周仓下高台。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00058",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "周仓"
      ],
      "text": "你们站起来！一五，一十，一、二、三。一十八骑残兵败将。",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00059",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "周仓上高台。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00060",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "军师呀，军师！你既能算，却不能料。慢说一十八骑残兵败将，就是一十八只猛虎，何足道哉！",
      "text_length": 42
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00061",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快二六板",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "我看他好一似鳌鱼吞钓，惊弓鸟插双翅也难飞逃。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00062",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "曹操"
      ],
      "text": "说什么我好似鳌鱼吞钓，说什么惊弓鸟也难飞逃。想当初待君侯恩高义好，上马金下马银美酒红袍。官封你汉寿亭侯爵禄不少，你本是大义人怎忘故交？",
      "text_length": 67
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00063",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "你虽然待我的恩高义好，我也曾答报了汗马功劳。斩颜良诛文丑立功报效，将印信悬高梁封金辞曹。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00064",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "曹操"
      ],
      "text": "我也曾命张辽文凭送到，临行时我又送美酒红袍。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00065",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "休提起送文凭令人可恼，诛孔秀，刺孟、韩，王植被枭。过黄河斩秦琪文凭才到，谢丞相假人情哪在心梢！",
      "text_length": 47
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00066",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 66,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "曹操"
      ],
      "text": "在许昌曾许我云阳答报，你本是大义人岂忘故交！",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03096003_e00067",
      "play_id": "03096003",
      "scene_id": "03096003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 67,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "非是我忘却了云阳答报，皆因你这奸曹罪恶难饶。在许田射鹿时把君欺藐，挟天子令诸侯势压群僚。逼死了董贵妃其罪非小，害董承斩马腾欲谋汉朝。恨不得拿住你剥皮楦草。上前来试一试偃月钢刀。",
      "text_length": 88
    },
    {
